metadata.name: Kalalau
metadata.description: Accessible only via a 22-mile trial that outlines the staggering silhouette of the Na Pali Coast lies Kalalau Beach. Even the wildest imagination could not conjure such jaw-dropping beauty â€“ cathedrals that dwarf the skyscrapers of Dubai and a waterfall that flows straight from the heavens. This 10-shot panorama attempts to capture the majesty of a Kalalau sunset.
